# lib/

Core library implementation for Intent, providing the command-line interface, steel thread management, agent system integration, and project configuration handling. This directory contains the main executable logic and support modules for Intent workflows.

## Dirs

- `commands/` -- Command implementations for steel threads, agents, configuration, and project initialization
- `support/` -- Utility modules for file operations, JSON handling, and system interaction

## Files

- `intent.ex` -- Main entry point and CLI dispatcher routing user commands to appropriate handlers
- `intent_cli.ex` -- Command-line argument parsing and option processing for Intent commands
- `agent_registry.ex` -- Agent system management with support for custom subagent installation and discovery
- `file_index.ex` -- File indexing system with checkbox state tracking for progress management
- `json_utils.ex` -- JSON serialization and deserialization utilities for configuration files
- `shell_utils.ex` -- Shell command execution and output handling for system integration
